title: No Icons
body: Why are people getting icons for free now and then and when i do the surveys and stuff i get no icons even if I've waited about 2-4 weeks

replies.body:
Which icons specifically are you talking about? 

The one for the Star Guardian quiz should theoretically have rolled out to everyone by now, but I'd give it a few more days anyway (and double check that it isn't anywhere in your icons, they don't always show up chronologically and the gift animation doesn't always play).
The icons from the Teemoing won't finish being distributed until "[up to two weeks after November 3, 2016 at 23:59 PT](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)."
